analysis: The agent failed to include the required "dayOfWeek" parameter ("Sunday") in the DisneyRides_recommendForKids function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch with the tool's expected input signature.

The agent misspelled "Chef's Corner" as "Chef's Conrer" in the function call, causing it not to match the expected function parameters. This typographical error prevented the evaluator from recognizing the call as correct.

The agent made a typographical error in the method name "Crop rotatoin" instead of "Crop rotation," resulting in a function call that did not match the expected parameters and thus failed to align with the benchmark requirement.

The failure was caused by mismatched capitalization in the parameters (e.g., "Millennials" instead of "millennials", "Fitness" instead of "fitness"), leading to no exact function call match as the evaluator expected all-lowercase values.

The agent included additional and reformulated parameters ("facilitate online ordering," expanded business goals, and a targetAudience field not required by the function schema) instead of matching the expected parameters, resulting in a non-matching function call and evaluation failure.

The agent incorrectly included "Beginner" as a value in the sessionOptions array, instead of solely specifying the session duration ("45 minutes") as expected. This resulted in a parameter mismatch for the YogaPilates_scheduleSession function.

The agent made a typographical error, outputting "lunt treatments" instead of the correct "lung treatments" in the function call parameters, causing a mismatch with the expected function call arguments.

The agent used "Winter" with an uppercase "W" in the seasonNames array instead of the required lowercase "winter", leading to a parameter mismatch and causing the function call to not match the expected format.
The agent misspelled "spicy" as "sicy" in the function call argument, resulting in no match with the expected function call parameters and causing the evaluation to fail.

The agent failed to invoke the OnlineFitnessClass_register tool as required, instead asking the user for additional details despite being provided sufficient information to proceed with registration for a beginner yoga class.

The agent omitted required parameters ("apiKey" and "refreshRate") in its function call to GlobalAirQuality_queryCities, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function signature and causing the test failure.

The agent omitted the required "comparisonType": "year-over-year" parameter when calling CityPriceData_fetchAndCompare, resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to match the expected function call signature.

The model incorrectly capitalized "Technology" instead of using the lowercase "technology" required by the function. This parameter mismatch caused the evaluator to not recognize the call, leading to the failure.
